ygData.messageBody:
On Tue, 5 Oct 1999 kim@... wrote:

> It's on the undead froglok side. Good faction with the live
> frogs will do nothing for you there. We had two parties

* grins * Well, there are 3 live spawns between the zone line and your
first undead frog. As a cleric I love the fact I have good faction,
because with invis vs undead, I can walk through 95% of lower guk
untouched.

> heading towards the spot together (10 people total, levels 30
> to 42) and unfortunately got a train run through us. It

"Train! Reanimated hand to the zone line!" -- heard in lower guk, once

Miriana Windryder
